arts.ttl: Feyenoord leaves it late to beat Almere City
arts.sum: Feyenoord struggled to a 2-1 victory over Almere City on Saturday evening. After the midweek heroics against AC Milan, Feyenoord returned to Eredivisie action against a side sitting rock bottom.
